Package cancellation

Interface Summary
Diagram.Decorator A Diagram decorator.
ICancellationDiagramAnalysis An analysis of all the cancellation Diagrams of a given (not necessarily quadratic) equation.
ICancellationDiagramAnalysisDecorator A decorator which adds features to an ICancellationDiagramAnalysis.
 

Class Summary
CancellationDiagramFactory Singleton factory for ICancellationDiagramAnalysis objects.
ComposableDiagramIterator An Iterator which is composable and can be used to lazily generate CancellationDiagrams.
Diagram  
DiagramDegeneracyTester Tests a Diagram for degeneracy.
DiagramTreeNode A node in the tree of all cancellation Diagrams.
DiagramTreeNodeComparator A Comparator which can order DiagramTreeNode objects.
Edge An Edge in a cancellation Diagram.
LabeledPath A path in the cancellation Diagram, together with its label.
LatexAdapter A singleton Factory for converting cancellation Diagrams into Latex formatted Strings.
Main  
Main2
